        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#faf5ff,#e9d8fd); width:100%; max-width:520px; margin:0 auto; height:380px; border-radius:20px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#553c9a; font-weight:800; font-size:1.1rem;">
          📖 Transcending Trauma
